item.title: About
item.description: 🧘‍ I’m beautiful. I’m strong. I’m powerful. ✈️ A gypsy soul and a vibrant hope for the unknown. #wanderlust 🖋 I love to sing and can play four musical instruments. 💻 I’m a software developer with an M.Sc. in Computer Science and passionate about computers, software programming and technology as a whole. 🐾 I have a pet cat 🐱 but I secretly like dogs.🐶 ♥️ I live to eat and love food.
